Class FieldBodyIND

              org.farng.mp3.lyrics3.FieldBodyIND
public class FieldBodyIND
extends AbstractLyrics3v2FieldBody

Indications field. This is always two characters big in v2.00, but might be bigger in a future standard. The first byte indicates wether or not a lyrics field is present. "1" for present and "0" for otherwise. The second character indicates if there is a timestamp in the lyrics. Again "1" for yes and "0" for no.
